sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 65: TikTok Shop Sync and Order Reconciliation Flow

  autonumber
  actor V as Vendor
  participant API as /api/social/sync/tiktok
  participant TT as TikTok Shop API
  participant Map as Catalog Mapping Store
  participant Order as Order Reconciliation Service
  participant Inv as Inventory Service
  participant Pay as Payout Attribution Service

  V->>API: Connect TikTok and sync catalog
  API->>TT: Push catalog mapping payload
  TT-->>API: Mapping status
  API->>Map: Save channel product mappings

  TT->>Order: External order webhook/event
  Order->>Map: Resolve external SKU to PRISM product
  alt Mapping conflict or missing
    Order-->>V: Manual reconciliation required
  else Mapping resolved
    Order->>Order: Idempotency check
    alt Duplicate external order
      Order-->>TT: 200 idempotent no-op
    else New order
      Order->>Inv: Decrement inventory
      Order->>Pay: Record channel payout attribution signal
      Pay-->>Order: Attribution persisted
      Order-->>V: Reconciled order created
    end
  end
